"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1121504","Home Office","false","2019-04-24","<p>Since November 2017, we have held monthly meetings with representatives from user groups, EU27 consular officials, Local Authorities, community groups and employers to help on the design and development of the EU Settlement Scheme.</p><p>Feedback since the full launch of the scheme on 30 March 2019 has been very positive and we continue to work closely with these representatives and other partners to ensure that the scheme is accessible and that we are able to reach all prospective applicants.</p>","Romsey and Southampton North","Caroline Nokes",,"2019-04-24T14:22:08.523Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1121504/answer","Biography information for Caroline Nokes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1121504/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1121504/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2019-04-11","Immigration: EU Nationals","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what representations he has received on the functioning of the EU Settled Status Scheme since 30 March 30 2019.","false","Biography information for Keith Vaz","Leicester East","Keith Vaz","244019"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1121505","Home Office","false","2019-04-24","<p>The Metropolitan Police have confirmed that the estimated cost of policing the Embassy between June 2012 and October 2015 was £13.2m. The Home Office does not hold any further information on this matter. It is an operational decision for the Metropolitan Police how to use their available resources.</p>","Ruislip, Northwood and Pinner","Mr Nick Hurd",,"2019-04-24T14:25:55.31Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1121505/answer","Biography information for Mr Nick Hurd","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1121505/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1121505/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2019-04-11","Julian Assange","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what the cost has been of the police operation to monitor Julian Assange since August 2012.","false","Biography information for Keith Vaz","Leicester East","Keith Vaz","244020"
